label: Bara kommun
description: Bara municipality, a former municipality of Sweden still appearing in some online datasets. Avoid using the short nameform as may cause confusion.

label: Heby kommun före 2007
description: Heby before 2007, when they changed county. Most of the time you would probably want to use Heby kommun even before 2007

label: Malung-Sälens kommun
description: Malung-Sälen municipality, formerly known as Malungs kommun

label: Uppsala kommun före 2003
description: Uppsala municipality before Knivsta broke away in 2003. Most of the time you would probably want to use Uppsala kommun even before 2003
